<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 21:13:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普可能会在关税攻势中转向经过考验的贸易法工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-likely-turn-tested-trade-law-tools-his-tariff-offensive-2024-11-27/</link><description>人们普遍预计，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将再次诉诸最喜欢的法律工具，以支持对墨西哥、加拿大和中国进口商品征收关税的威胁：《国际紧急经济权力法案》，这是实施其更广泛关税议程的几个法律途径之一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 18:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-likely-turn-tested-trade-law-tools-his-tariff-offensive-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对关税下了高风险、高回报的赌注，以遏制芬太尼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-places-high-risk-high-reward-bet-tariffs-stem-fentanyl-2024-11-27/</link><description>专家表示，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普誓言要对中国和墨西哥征收关税，除非它们阻止芬太尼和移民越过美国边境流动，这可能会促使这些国家政府在缉毒警务方面进行更深入的合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 16:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-places-high-risk-high-reward-bet-tariffs-stem-fentanyl-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟国家支持对中国钛白粉征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-countries-back-duties-chinese-titanium-dioxide-2024-11-27/</link><description>据了解欧盟调查情况的消息人士透露，欧盟成员国周三为欧盟对从中国进口的二氧化钛（TiO2）征收明确的反倾销税扫清了道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 15:13:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-countries-back-duties-chinese-titanium-dioxide-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯表示如果美国在日本部署导弹俄罗斯将做出回应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-it-will-respond-if-us-places-missiles-japan-2024-11-27/</link><description>俄罗斯周三表示，如果美国在日本部署导弹，这将威胁俄罗斯的安全，并促使莫斯科采取报复行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 14:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-it-will-respond-if-us-places-missiles-japan-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>经过多年的外交努力，中国释放了三名美国公民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-brokers-release-three-americans-imprisoned-china-politico-reports-2024-11-27/</link><description>白宫周三表示，中国已经释放了美国公民马克·斯维丹(Mark Swidan)、李凯(Kai Li)和梁约翰(John Leung)，结束了多年来针对华盛顿称在中国被错误拘留的美国人的外交努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:55:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-brokers-release-three-americans-imprisoned-china-politico-reports-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>宜家高管表示，贸易关税使保持低价变得更加困难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trade-tariffs-make-it-harder-keep-prices-low-ikea-executive-says-2024-11-27/</link><description>全球最大家具零售商首席财务官周三对路透社表示，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普计划的关税将使宜家更难保持低价。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trade-tariffs-make-it-harder-keep-prices-low-ikea-executive-says-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>预言家阿萨尼击中制胜球，光州队在亚冠联赛中保持第二名</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/prophetic-asani-hits-winner-gwangju-stay-second-asian-champions-league-2024-11-27/</link><description>替补出场的贾西尔·阿萨尼首次触球得分，帮助光州足球俱乐部以 1-0 战胜上海申花队，横滨水手队击败浦项制铁队，帮助韩国队在亚冠精英联赛阶段保持第二名。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/prophetic-asani-hits-winner-gwangju-stay-second-asian-champions-league-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>德国为中国企业提供更多投资担保</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/germany-issues-more-investment-guarantees-business-china-2024-11-27/</link><description>德国经济部的数据显示，德国政府对华投资的国家担保价值在经历大幅下降后，今年有所上升。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:42:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/germany-issues-more-investment-guarantees-business-china-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>教宗每周接见活动将于12月起翻译成中文</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/popes-weekly-audiences-be-translated-into-mandarin-december-2024-11-27/</link><description>教皇方济各周三表示，从下周开始，他在梵蒂冈每周公开接见时的教义也将被翻译成中文。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/popes-weekly-audiences-be-translated-into-mandarin-december-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国假期将焦点转向通胀，法国局势紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-27/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在曼哈顿唯一的选举胜利是在下东区的这个街区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-only-manhattan-electoral-win-is-this-block-lower-east-side-2024-11-27/</link><description>唯一的例外是下东区的一个街区，这里曾经是苏联间谍朱利叶斯·罗森伯格和埃塞尔·罗森伯格的家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-only-manhattan-electoral-win-is-this-block-lower-east-side-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>小马智行纳斯达克首秀股价大涨15% 估值52.5亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-robotaxi-startup-pony-ai-raises-260-mln-us-ipo-2024-11-27/</link><description>周三，小马智行的股价开盘较发行价高出约 15%，这家机器人出租车公司的估值达到 52.5 亿美元，这表明投资者对中国公司持积极态度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 10:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-robotaxi-startup-pony-ai-raises-260-mln-us-ipo-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，10月份国外智能手机在华销量同比下降44.25%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foreign-smartphone-sales-china-drop-4425-oct-data-shows-2024-11-27/</link><description>一家政府下属的研究公司周三发布的数据显示，10月份包括苹果公司iPhone在内的外国品牌智能手机在中国的销量同比下降了44.25%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/foreign-smartphone-sales-china-drop-4425-oct-data-shows-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国称国防部长董军接受调查的报道是“追影子”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-calls-report-that-defence-minister-dong-jun-is-under-probe-shadow-chasing-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国外交部周三在回应有关中国国防部长董军因腐败接受调查的报道的问题时表示，这“只是追影子”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-calls-report-that-defence-minister-dong-jun-is-under-probe-shadow-chasing-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国禾赛明年将激光雷达价格减半，预计将在电动汽车中广泛采用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-hesai-halve-lidar-prices-next-year-sees-wide-adoption-electric-cars-2024-11-27/</link><description>全球最大的自动驾驶激光雷达传感器制造商中国禾赛集团表示，计划明年将其主要产品的价格削减一半，这将导致该技术在电动汽车中得到更广泛的采用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 06:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-hesai-halve-lidar-prices-next-year-sees-wide-adoption-electric-cars-2024-11-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>